                        <i class="bi bi-film"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Кинотеатр</h3>
                    <p>Современный кинотеатр с комфортными залами и отличным звуком</p>
                </div>
                <div class="advantage-card">
                    <div class="advantage-icon">
                        <i class="bi bi-balloon"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Детская зона</h3>
                    <p>Безопасное и интересное пространство для детей разных возрастов</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-section team-section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2 class="section-title">Руководство</h2>
                <div class="title-decoration"><span></span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="team-slider">
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-image">
                        <img src="/images/placeholder.svg" alt="Иванов Иван Иванович">
                        <div class="team-social">
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3>Иванов Иван</h3>
                        <p class="team-position">Генеральный директор</p>
                        <p class="team-quote">"Мы создаём пространство, где каждый найдёт что-то для себя"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-image">
                        <img src="/images/placeholder.svg" alt="Петрова Анна Сергеевна">
                        <div class="team-social">
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3>Петрова Анна</h3>
                        <p class="team-position">Коммерческий директор</p>
                        <p class="team-quote">"Наша цель - предложить лучший выбор для наших посетителей"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="team-card">
                    <div class="team-image">
                        <img src="/images/placeholder.svg" alt="Сидоров Алексей Петрович">
                        <div class="team-social">
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-linkedin"></i></a>
                            <a href="#" class="social-link"><i class="bi bi-envelope"></i></a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-info">
                        <h3>Сидоров Алексей</h3>
                        <p class="team-position">Технический директор</p>
                        <p class="team-quote">"Комфорт и безопасность - наш приоритет"</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="about-section cta-section">
            <div class="cta-card">
                <div class="cta-content">
                    <h2>Приходите к нам за покупками и отличным настроением!</h2>
                    <p>Ждём вас ежедневно с 10:00 до 22:00</p>
                    <div class="cta-buttons">
                        <a href="/map" class="btn btn-primary">Схема ТРЦ</a>
                        <a href="/shops" class="btn btn-outline">Магазины</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

<style>
/* Основные стили страницы "О нас" */
.about-page-main {
    background-color: #cfe8f7;
    background-image: linear-gradient(135deg, #cfe8f7 0%, #a6d4f2 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

/* Декоративные элементы фона */
.decoration-circle {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    z-index: 0;
}

.circle-1 {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    top: -100px;
    left: -100px;
}

.circle-2 {
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    bottom: -200px;
    right: -200px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
}

.circle-3 {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    top: 30%;
    right: 10%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
}

/* Заголовки секций */
.section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    position: relative;
}

.section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1976D2, #64B5F6);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 3px 15px rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.3);
}

.section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a4971;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}

.title-decoration {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 1rem;
}

.title-decoration span {
    width: 70px;
    height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1976D2, #64B5F6);
    border-radius: 10px;
}

/* Герой-секция */
.about-hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.hero-content {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
    animation: fadeInLeft 1s ease-out;
}

@keyframes fadeInLeft {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-30px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
    }
}

.hero-title {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1a4971;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
}

.hero-text {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
}

.stat-item {
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 100px;
}

.stat-number {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #1976D2;
    line-height: 1;
}

.stat-label {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.hero-image {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 300px;
    position: relative;
    animation: fadeInRight 1s ease-out;
}

@keyframes fadeInRight {
    from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(30px);
    }
    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
    }
}

.about-main-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    border: 10px solid white;
}

.image-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top right, rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.3), transparent);
    border-radius: 20px;
    pointer-events: none;
}

.image-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 30px;
    right: 30px;
    background: white;
    color: #1976D2;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* Секция миссии */
.mission-section {
    margin: 6rem 0;
}

.mission-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-top: 5px solid #1976D2;
}

.mission-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1976D2, #64B5F6);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    position: absolute;
    top: -40px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.4);
}

.mission-text {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #555;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
}

/* Секция преимуществ */
.advantages-section {
    margin: 6rem 0;
}

.advantages-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
}

.advantage-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

.advantage-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    background: white;
}

.advantage-icon {
    width: 70px;
    height: 70px;
    background: #bbdefb;
    border-radius: 15px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2rem;
    color: #1565C0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.advantage-card:hover .advantage-icon {
    background: #1976D2;
    color: white;
    transform: scale(1.1);
}

.advantage-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.advantage-card p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

/* Секция команды */
.team-section {
    margin: 6rem 0;
}

.team-slider {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
}

.team-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 15px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    width: 320px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.team-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
}

.team-image {
    height: 300px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.team-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}

.team-card:hover .team-image img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

.team-social {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -50px;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.6), transparent);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.team-card:hover .team-social {
    bottom: 0;
}

.social-link {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: white;
    color: #1976D2;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.social-link:hover {
    background: #1976D2;
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
}

.team-info {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
}

.team-info h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.team-position {
    color: #1976D2;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.team-quote {
    color: #666;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
}

/* CTA секция */
.cta-section {
    margin: 4rem 0 2rem;
}

.cta-card {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1565C0, #64B5F6);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(25, 118, 210, 0.3);
    text-align: center;
}

.cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

.cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.btn {
    padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
}

.btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: #1565C0;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: white;
    color: white;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
}

.btn-outline {
    background: transparent;
    border-color: white;
    color: white;
}

.btn-outline:hover {
    background: white;
    color: #1565C0;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
}

/* Медиа-запросы */
@media (max-width: 992px) {
    .hero-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .about-hero {
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .hero-image {
        order: -1;
    }
    
    .about-main-image {
        height: 350px;
    }
    
    .mission-card {
        padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page-main {
        padding: 3rem 0;
    }
    
    .hero-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .section-title {
        font-size: 2rem;
    }
    
    .stat-number {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    
    .mission-text {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    
    .cta-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    
    .advantage-card {
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .advantage-icon {
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        font-size: 1.7rem;
    }
    
    .team-card {
        width: 100%;
    }
}
</style>

